==English==
===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-teenager.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''teenager'''

# {{italbrac|countable}} Literally, a [[child]] from thir''teen'' and nine''teen''.

====Usage notes====
Sometimes only refers up to the legal [[US]] [[minor]] limit of eigh''teen'' years-old.

===Notes===
*In the earlier years, sometimes referred to as a [[youth]]; in later years, sometimes referred to as a [[young adult]].

